name: RIP HEN #001
description:
Hic et Nunc is dead. But is it really?

We want to wrap up 2021 by remembering the "RIP HEN" first exhibit featuring the Fakewhale Collection, curated by Jesse Draxler that took place near Switzerland, in the Valuart Gallery, on December 14th, 2021.

It is with great pleasure that we share the poster of this historic event in the form of an NFT to all artists, staff and team that have made this exhibition come to life.
